<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I've camped the Ishva Mal for my robe for more hours than I care to recall, and I can say with a good bit of certainty that the brains are an always drop on the Ishva. The scroll seems to be quite common too. <BR>
<BR>
The robe on the other hand...<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Oh, and there weren't any clerics camping with me, so the brains were always destroyed.<BR>
<BR>
Candaar<BR>
37th Enchanter of Tarew Marr<BR>
Dragonkin<BR>
